src:
O'Rourke ends bid to be Democratic presidential nomination - video
02 Nov 2019, 10:43 by AP



The former Texas congressman announced on Friday that he was ending his campaign, which failed to recapture the enthusiasm, interest and fundraising prowess of his 2018 Senate race


Beto O'Rourke withdraws from Democratic race to face Trump
